  "description": "Answers \"how long to get there?\" and \"how far before nightfall?\" from one calculator: enter a distance to get the travel time, or a time budget to get the distance, at Fast, Normal, or Slow pace. It pulls speed from a mount or vehicle's own stats, works in imperial or metric, and posts to chat with the pace's Stealth and Perception penalties.",
